headline.main: Russia: 1 Dead, 3 Detained in Operation Against IS Cell
headline.print_headline: Russia: 1 Dead, 3 Detained in Operation Against IS Cell

lead_paragraph: Russian authorities say one person has been killed and three others detained in an operation to break up a sleeper cell of the Islamic State in the country's restive southern region of Dagestan.
